videos.description: Clemsons Aamir Simms gets off a three pointer before the half and gets a fortunate bounce for the bucket.
videos.headline: Simms gets a lucky bounce to hit 3-pointer

videos.description: Clemson's Shelton Mitchell steals the ball and dishes it to Clyde Trapp for the dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: Trapp gets easy bucket off steal

videos.description: Quinndary Weatherspoon's 3-pointer is the 18th of the game, which sets a new school record for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon sinks Mississippi State's 18th 3 of game
